  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;transmutation;\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;alchemist 2, bloodrager 2, druid 2, hunter 2, occultist 2, sorcerer/wizard 2;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M/DF (a tiny ball of tar)<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;touch<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;creature touched<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;10 minutes/level (D)<br>\n      <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will negates (harmless);&nbsp;\n      <strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>The subject's grip and footing become sure, granting a +4 competence bonus on Climb checks, on Acrobatics checks to balance, and to CMD against bull rush, drag, reposition, and trip attempts. While affected by this spell, the target is also immune to the disarm combat maneuver.</p>\n</div>\n"
